Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.79,0:01:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}遥かな君まで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.28,0:01:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,2000)}残さず伝えて　きっと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.60,0:22:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}だんご　だんご　だんご　だんご
